00:21:41.996 --> 00:21:43.370
Is there some
angle that we could

00:21:43.370 --> 00:21:45.320
use to take some of the
stuff that Google is good at

00:21:45.320 --> 00:21:46.903
and that we're all
good at technically

00:21:46.903 --> 00:21:48.870
to help the problem?

