again, that I wanted to share

00:24:33.150 --> 00:24:36.850
is that we are facing an
unprecedented global crisis

00:24:36.850 --> 00:24:39.610
with 65 million people
who have been displaced

00:24:39.610 --> 00:24:40.732
by violence and conflict.

00:24:40.732 --> 00:24:42.440
That's more than at
any point since we've

00:24:42.440 --> 00:24:44.120
been counting in history.

00:24:44.120 --> 00:24:46.710
And the average amount of
time that someone is a refugee

00:24:46.710 --> 00:24:48.200
