00:24:48.200 --> 00:24:50.880
So we need to think,
as a community,

00:24:50.880 --> 00:24:53.620
about new ways of doing
things, not just giving

00:24:53.620 --> 00:24:56.050
aid year after year
after year because

00:24:56.050 --> 00:24:59.000
