run out of money to do that.

00:24:59.000 --> 00:25:00.980
So how do we get
people to places

00:25:00.980 --> 00:25:02.880
where they don't
need aid anymore

00:25:02.880 --> 00:25:04.900
and they can become
contributors?

00:25:04.900 --> 00:25:06.750
And we have such
a moral obligation

00:25:06.750 --> 00:25:08.990
to do this for all those
people that are in danger,

00:25:08.990 --> 00:25:11.780
but in particular,
for children who

00:25:11.780 --> 00:25:15.660
are impacted by these
crises and just need

00:25:15.660 --> 00:25:18.530
